org.jsonurl.factory

Interface Parser<V,C extends V,ABT,A extends C,JBT,J extends C,B extends V,M extends V,N extends V,S extends V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - value type (any JSON value)
    C - composite type (array or object)
    A - array type
    ABT - array builder type
    J - object type
    JBT - object builder type
    B - boolean type
    M - number type
    N - null type
    S - string type
    All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Parser.TransparentBuilder<V,C,A,J,B,M,N,S>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonUrlParser, JsonUrlParser, JsonUrlParser, ValueFactoryParser, ValueFactoryParser.TransparentBuilder

    public interface Parser<V,C extends V,ABT,A extends C,JBT,J extends C,B extends V,M extends V,N extends V,S extends V>
extends JsonUrlOptionable
    A JSON→URL text parser.

    An instance of this interface may be used to parse JSON→URL text to build values bound to a specific data model API. Each instance maintains a set of limits that are applied any time the one of the parse() methods is invoked.

    Since:
    2019-09-01
    Author:
    jsonurl.org, David MacCormack
